name: WoogieWoo
overview:
WoogieWoo is a place for designers (Brands, Artists, Vintage, and Handmade). A simple E-commerce solution that allows designers to create a free shop and sell their items to new and existing customers.

The WoogieWoo marketplace is home to thousands of unique pieces created by designers around the world. All items in the marketplace are also distributed into designers unique and customizable shops.

As a member on WoogieWoo you can follow your favorite designers and track their latest product uploads. Navigate freely from customized shops using the WoogieWoo toolbar. Or browse new and interesting designers from around the world.
